'''Holm'starn''' was a city on the [[Bothan/Legends|Bothan]] [[Homeworld/Legends|homeworld]] of [[Bothawui/Legends|Bothawui]]. 

It was located in the northwestern peninsula of the [[Planet/Legends|planet's]] eastern continent. [[Mesdri'starn]] was to be found far to the southeast.

